Codex Termux is a porting/distribution fork of OpenAI Codex for Android ARM64
(Termux). It carries only the Android/Termux compatibility delta needed to
package and run upstream Codex on Termux. These compatibility patches are
maintained by Davide A. Guglielmi and distributed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0 together with the upstream Codex codebase.

